51.9	Emir_Kusturica	Emir Kusturica	Emir Nemanja Kusturica ; born 24 November 1954 in Sarajevo) is a Serbian filmmaker, actor and musician, recognized for several internationally acclaimed feature films. He is a two-time winner of the Palme d'Or at Cannes (for When Father Was Away on Business and Underground), as well as being a Commander of the French Ordre des Arts et des Lettres.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/da/Emir_Kusturica_at_Guadalajara_film_festival_2009.jpg/250px-Emir_Kusturica_at_Guadalajara_film_festival_2009.jpg
